name: Infinite Harmony Beams Set 03 with 03 Sound Percussion
description:
HTML5 file is suitable for interactive art galleries. Once the page is loaded a gravity function is triggered and the bars fall up and down. One beam that touches the ground triggers a sound. Eight variations that are all executed at the same time create a calming melody composition. This is a variation/collection of eight 3/8 hmlt5audiovisual.

Press "SPACE" or "MOUSE LEFT" for replay.
